      "description": "Offered is an exceptional E46 M3, a pinnacle of atmospheric engineering. At its heart lies the S54 3.2L inline-six, featuring individual throttle bodies and high-pressure dual-VANOS variable valve timing, delivering a linear power band to an 8,000 RPM redline. This specimen boasts a reinforced rear subframe and a perfectly calibrated M-variable differential lock for optimal torque distribution. The suspension maintains factory-spec kinematics with fresh bushings and original damping rates. Every mechanical interface, from the Getrag 6-speed linkage to the cross-drilled compound rotors, operates with tactile precision. A truly turn-key, investment-grade icon with zero rod-bearing issues or subframe fatigue.",
